data.title: My Hero: Brigitte
data.description: In this episode of My Hero, hear from Dallas Fuel's ZachaREEE, Vancouver Titans' Haksal, and Los Angeles Valiant's Agilities as they break down Brigitte's kit. It's all part of Insights: powered by Intel. Want more Insights? Visit https://overwatchleague.com/en-us/intel-insights.
